      "page_number": 20,
      "section": "act_three",
      "speaker": "pixel",
      "speaker_mode": "narration",
      "text": "We stood in the Garden of Stones as the grey filtered light of the Shattered Span played across ice formations. The wind whistled through frozen passages. Somewhere distant, ice cracked and fell and no one would ever know what it had been.",
