      "page_number": 20,
      "section": "act_three",
      "speaker": "arc",
      "speaker_mode": "dialogue",
      "text": "Arc was silent for a long time. Then: Miss Paradox, I find I would very much like to return to Chronicle Hall. I have research to conduct. Questions to ask. Memories to... to audit.",
