      "page_number": 20,
      "section": "act_three",
      "speaker": "arc",
      "speaker_mode": "dialogue",
      "text": "An excellent point. I've stopped trying to calculate odds where you're concerned, Miss Paradox. The mathematics consistently fail to account for your particular brand of stubborn hope.",
